    "rich_text_k7z6De": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_4qWJN6": {
          "type": "heading",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "About ORI GVM Upgrades",
            "highlight_style": "none",
            "enable_highlight_text_color": false,
            "heading_size": "h0",
            "heading_color": ""
          }
        },
        "text_7BUCdz": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Maximize Your Payload & Towing: ORI GVM & GCM Upgrades for American Trucks</h3><p>American trucks are built incredibly tough—but when they hit Australian shores, their factory GVM (Gross Vehicle Mass) and GCM (Gross Combined Mass) ratings often fall short of what you actually need to carry and tow. By the time you add steel bullbars, custom tray bodies, heavy canopies, long-range fuel tanks, and serious camping gear, those factory limits add up fast.</p><p>Exceeding your GVM or GCM isn't just a massive insurance risk—it's a strict legal liability that compromises your safety.</p><p>That’s where our <strong>ORI certified GVM and GCM upgrade packages</strong> come in. Engineered specifically for your favorite full-size American trucks, our premium upgrades give you a higher legal payload and towing capacity. This means you can load up your rig and hitch up your caravan properly, without ever having to compromise on gear.</p><p><strong>Why Choose an ORI GVM & GCM Upgrade?</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Legally Increase Your Capacities:</strong> Safely maximize both your Gross Vehicle Mass and Gross Combined Mass ratings to handle real-world touring and towing weights.</li><li><strong>Fully ADR Compliant:</strong> Road-registered and 100% legal across all Australian states and territories.</li><li><strong>Australian Engineered:</strong> Rigorously tested, engineered, and certified by industry-leading Australian automotive engineers.</li><li><strong>Protect Your Assets:</strong> Ensures your heavy-duty truck remains fully insured and keeps you completely on the right side of the law.</li><li><strong>Purpose-Tuned Suspension:</strong> Features premium, heavy-duty suspension components specifically matched and tuned for harsh Australian conditions.</li><li><strong>Uncompromised Ride Quality:</strong> Expertly designed to handle massive loads while maintaining—or even enhancing—the manufacturer's original ride comfort and handling characteristics.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
